summary:
HostCircle is reselling IP transit / transport services from several Tier-1 carriers. Contact us if you are looking to cut your transit costs!

We also offers high bandwidth hosting solutions in 12 countries. Our solutions specializes for VOD, OTT TV and CDN companies. HostCircle is one of the cheapest high bandwidth solution provider in the market. For over 10 years we have helped business reduce their operating cost by providing affordable high bandwidth solutions. 

PS: We are hiring for several positions. https://angel.co/hostcircle/jobs for open positions.
